snippet.title: Shark Tank Nepal | Season 1 | Episode 01 | Grand Premiere
snippet.description:
Shark Tank Nepal is the first-ever Nepali edition of the globally acclaimed business reality show.
The 20-episode season will showcase Nepal's most promising entrepreneurs pitching their business ideas to a panel of successful business leaders ("Sharks") for potential investment and mentorship. 

बिश्वप्रसिद्ध बिजनेस रियालिटी टीभी शो शार्क ट्यांकको नेपालका संस्करण शार्क ट्यांक नेपाल सुरु भइसकेको छ ।
पहिलो सिजनमा ११० जना उद्यमीले आफ्नो ब्यबसायलाई शार्कसामू पेश गर्ने अबसर पाएका छन् ।
